GS (Pitch or business model)

Short version

Save grocery lists online

PROBLEM
1_ Not easy to create and share shopping list online
2_ Building food tech startup can take a lot of time and money


SOLUTION
1_ Use our pre-populated grocery lists(diets, gluthen-free, health options)
2_ Use our platform as starting point. Speed up development process

Audience
1_ People that want to plan their shopping budget
People that want to weight loss or be health by tracking their meals
2_ Startup owners that want to include our functionality or extend their business with new tools, features.


Monetization
advertising
Saas model
Exclusive deals(in cooperation with other businesses)

